<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Understanding Your Tax Resolution Options</title>
    <style>
      body,
      table,
      td,
      p,
      a {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }
      body {
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        font-family: "Helvetica Neue", Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
      }
      img {
        border: 0;
        display: block;
        outline: none;
        text-decoration: none;
      }
      .email-wrapper {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #f4f6f9;
        padding: 30px 0;
      }
      .email-container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        overflow: hidden;
        box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
      }
      .email-header {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 30px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-header img {
        max-width: 200px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto;
      }
      .hero-banner {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #1a2744 0%, #2c4a7c 100%);
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .hero-banner h1 {
        color: #ffffff;
        font-size: 22px;
        font-weight: 700;
        line-height: 1.3;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .hero-banner p {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        font-size: 15px;
        margin-top: 8px;
      }
      .email-body {
        padding: 36px 40px;
        color: #333333;
      }
      .email-body p {
        font-size: 15px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 16px;
        color: #444444;
      }
      .greeting {
        font-size: 17px;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: #1a2744;
        margin-bottom: 12px;
      }
      .option-card {
        background-color: #f8fafc;
        border: 1px solid #e2e8f0;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 18px 20px;
        margin-bottom: 14px;
      }
      .option-title {
        font-size: 15px;
        font-weight: 700;
        color: #1a2744;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .option-desc {
        font-size: 13px;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      .cta-wrapper {
        text-align: center;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .cta-button {
        display: inline-block;
        background-color: #2c4a7c;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-size: 16px;
        font-weight: 600;
        text-decoration: none;
        padding: 14px 36px;
        border-radius: 6px;
      }
      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid #e8ecf1;
        margin: 28px 0;
      }
      .callout-box {
        background-color: #fffbeb;
        border-left: 4px solid #d4a017;
        border-radius: 4px;
        padding: 18px 22px;
        margin: 24px 0;
      }
      .callout-box p {
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #6b5a00;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
      }
      .email-footer {
        background-color: #1a2744;
        padding: 28px 40px;
        text-align: center;
      }
      .email-footer p {
        color: #8fa3bf;
        font-size: 12px;
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }
      .email-footer a {
        color: #b8c9e0;
        text-decoration: underline;
      }
      .footer-phone {
        font-size: 16px !important;
        color: #ffffff !important;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        margin-bottom: 12px !important;
      }
      @media only screen and (max-width: 620px) {
        .email-body,
        .email-header,
        .hero-banner,
        .email-footer {
          padding-left: 24px !important;
          padding-right: 24px !important;
        }
        .hero-banner h1 {
          font-size: 20px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="email-wrapper">
      <table
        class="email-container"
        role="presentation"
        cellpadding="0"
        cellspacing="0"
        width="100%"
      >
        <tr><td class="email-header"><img
              src="cid:emailLogo"
              alt="Tax Advocate Group"
            /></td></tr>
        <tr><td class="hero-banner">
            <h1>You Have More Options Than You Think</h1>
            <p>A quick look at how tax resolution actually works</p>
          </td></tr>
        <tr><td class="email-body">
            <p class="greeting">Hi {{name}},</p>
            <p>One of the most common things we hear from new clients is, "I
              didn't know I had options." The truth is, the IRS and most state
              agencies have established programs designed specifically to help
              taxpayers resolve outstanding balances &mdash; but understanding
              which ones apply to you can be confusing without the right
              guidance.</p>
            <p>Here's a high-level look at some of the paths our team evaluates
              for every client:</p>
            <div class="option-card">
              <div class="option-title">&#128176; Structured Payment
                Arrangements</div>
              <div class="option-desc">Formalized agreements that allow you to
                pay your balance over time in manageable monthly amounts, often
                with reduced penalties accruing while you're in compliance.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="option-card">
              <div class="option-title">&#128221; Settlement Programs</div>
              <div class="option-desc">In qualifying cases, the IRS may accept
                less than the full amount owed. Eligibility depends on your
                financial situation, and our team handles the analysis and
                paperwork involved.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="option-card">
              <div class="option-title">&#128203; Compliance &amp; Filing
                Assistance</div>
              <div class="option-desc">If you have unfiled returns, getting
                compliant is often the critical first step before any resolution
                program can move forward. We help you get current quickly and
                accurately.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="option-card">
              <div class="option-title">&#128737; Protection from Enforcement</div>
              <div class="option-desc">Facing a levy, lien, or garnishment?
                There are procedures to pause or release enforcement actions
                while a resolution is being worked out. Timing is critical, and
                we move fast.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="option-card">
              <div class="option-title">&#9878;&#65039; Penalty &amp; Interest
                Review</div>
              <div class="option-desc">Many clients qualify for reduction of
                penalties and, in some cases, interest. We review your account
                for any applicable relief that may lower your total balance.</div>
            </div>
            <div class="callout-box">
              <p><strong>&#9888;&#65039; Important:</strong>
                The right option depends entirely on your specific numbers and
                circumstances. What works for one taxpayer may not apply to
                another. That's why a personalized consultation is the best
                first step &mdash; it costs nothing and gives you clarity.</p>
            </div>
            <p>Our job is to evaluate every available program, determine which
              ones you qualify for, and recommend the strategy that puts you in
              the strongest position. You don't need to figure this out alone.</p>
            <div class="cta-wrapper"><a
                href="{{scheduleUrl}}"
                class="cta-button"
              >Let's Review Your Options</a></div>
            <p style="text-align:center; font-size:14px; color:#666;">Or call us
              toll-free:
              <strong style="color:#1a2744;">{{phone}}</strong></p>
            <hr class="divider" />
            <p style="font-size:13px; color:#888; line-height:1.6;">You're
              receiving this email because you recently expressed interest in
              Tax Advocate Group. If you'd prefer not to receive follow-ups,
              simply reply and let us know.</p>
          </td></tr>
        <tr><td class="email-footer">
            <p class="footer-phone">&#128222; {{phone}}</p>
            <p><strong style="color:#fff;">Tax Advocate Group</strong></p>
            <p>Tax Resolution &amp; Relief Services</p>
            <p style="margin-top:10px;"><a
                href="https://www.taxadvocategroup.com"
              >taxadvocategroup.com</a></p>
            <p style="margin-top:14px; font-size:11px; color:#6b829e;">&copy;
              {{year}}
              Tax Advocate Group. All rights reserved.</p>
          </td></tr>
      </table>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>